This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The paper discusses the equivalence between policy gradient methods and soft Q-learning, which are both model-free reinforcement learning algorithms. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). Other likely sub-categories include cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.RO (Robotics), cs.SY (Systems and Control), and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), as these sub-categories are also relevant to reinforcement learning.
